 Crypto Rules Everything Around Me - C.R.E.A.M. Finance is a decentralized lending protocol for individuals,
institutions and protocols to access financial services. Part of the yearn
finance ecosystem, it is a permissionless, open source and blockchain agnostic
protocol serving users on Ethereum, BNB Chain, Polygon and Fantom. Users who
are passively holding ETH or wBTC can deposit their assets on C.R.E.A.M. to
earn yield, similar to a traditional savings account.
